{"sn8.12:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 8.12 ","sn8.12:0.2":"1. Vangisavagga ","sn8.12:0.3":"Vangisasutta ","sn8.12:1.1":"Ekam samayam ayasma vangiso savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","sn8.12:1.2":"Tena kho pana samayena ayasma vangiso aciraarahattappatto hutva vimuttisukham patisamvedi tayam velayam ima gathayo abhasi: ","sn8.12:2.1":"“Kaveyyamatta vicarimha pubbe, ","sn8.12:2.2":"Gama gamam pura puram; ","sn8.12:2.3":"Athaddasama sambuddham, ","sn8.12:2.4":"Saddha no upapajjatha. ","sn8.12:3.1":"So me dhammamadesesi, ","sn8.12:3.2":"khandhayatanadhatuyo; ","sn8.12:3.3":"Tassaham dhammam sutvana, ","sn8.12:3.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","sn8.12:4.1":"Bahunnam vata atthaya, ","sn8.12:4.2":"bodhim ajjhagama muni; ","sn8.12:4.3":"Bhikkhunam bhikkhuninanca, ","sn8.12:4.4":"ye niyamagataddasa. ","sn8.12:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","sn8.12:5.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","sn8.12:5.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","sn8.12:5.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","sn8.12:6.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","sn8.12:6.2":"Dibbacakkhum visodhitam; ","sn8.12:6.3":"Tevijjo iddhipattomhi, ","sn8.12:6.4":"Cetopariyayakovido”ti. ","sn8.12:7.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn8.12:7.1":"Nikkhantam arati ceva, ","sn8.12:7.2":"pesala atimannana; ","sn8.12:7.3":"Anandena subhasita, ","sn8.12:7.4":"sariputtapavarana; ","sn8.12:7.5":"Parosahassam kondanno, ","sn8.12:7.6":"moggallanena gaggara; ","sn8.12:7.7":"Vangisena dvadasati. ","sn8.12:7.8":"Vangisasamyuttam samattam. "}